snippet.textDisplay:
I know very little of music. My little daughter is learning music and is struggling with the note identification each day. Listening to this Composition given me hope that may be some day my girl can play and juggle with the note the way the singer Harish ramakrishnan was doing.
Great team and amazing energy everyone. Amid today's composition which only increases. Decibels and races heart rate creating noise, this Tarana took the best of the two worlds. And as a listener I try hard to keep my eyes open but it's so enchanting that I seldom could keep them open. Continue creating such magic. Thank you.
snippet.textOriginal:
